{"word":"Virgin","slug":"virgin","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Virgin</b> Proofs of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=22&verse=21'>Deu 22:21</a><br/> Dowry of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=22&verse=17'>Exo 22:17</a><br/> Character of, to be protected<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=22&verse=21'>Deu 22:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=22&verse=24'>Deu 22:24</a><br/> Betrothal of, a quasi marriage<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=22&verse=24'>Deu 22:24</a><br/> Distinguishing apparel of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=13&verse=18'>2Sa 13:18</a><br/> Priests might marry none but<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=21&verse=14'>Lev 21:14</a><br/> Mourn in the temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=25&chapter=1&verse=4'>Lam 1:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=25&chapter=2&verse=10'>Lam 2:10</a><br/> Virginity of, bewailed<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=11&verse=39'>Jdg 11:39</a><br/> Parable of the wise and foolish<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=25&verse=13'>Mat 25:13</a><br/> Mother of Jesus a virgin<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=7&verse=14'>Isa 7:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=1&verse=23'>Mat 1:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=1&verse=27'>Luk 1:27</a><br/> Advised by Paul not to marry<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=7'>1Ch 7</a><br/> Figurative:<br/> - Of the church<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=62&verse=5'>Isa 62:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=14&verse=17'>Jer 14:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=31&vers